<h2 class="bold font-l">Beast Maker</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
The Beast Maker homeworld is a gigantic swamp, with green and black ooze that easily traps any creature smaller than a Beast Maker dragon and suffocates it. Small patches of dry ground harbor wooden huts which serve as homes for the natives, and they are connected by split logs floating in the ooze in between. The horizon is shrouded in an ominous black mist, adding to the eerie feel of the realm. Torches are lit all over to provide lighting. In the middle of the realm is a huge Aztec-like temple with numerous steps. It is used for meetings among the inhabitants. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/BubblegloopSwamp" class='trope-example-link'>Bubblegloop Swamp</a></p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="b6admk" data-video-descrip="In the 100% Completion ending, Gnasty Gnorc refreezes all of the other dragons, thus Spyro has to do his adventure all over again." data-video-title="Spyro the Dragon (1998)" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/b6admk_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/b6admk.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/HereWeGoAgain" data-video-tropename="Here We Go Again!" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="VideoGame/SpyroTheDragon1998" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/b6admk.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">Spyro the Drago...</span></p>
</a>
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="vs9nuk" data-video-descrip="Gnasty Gnorc is the one responsible for the dragons being encased in stone and is the main antagonist of the first Spyro game." data-video-title="Gnasty Gnorc" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/vs9nuk_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/vs9nuk.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/BigBad" data-video-tropename="Big Bad" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="VideoGame/SpyroTheDragon1998" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/vs9nuk.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">Gnasty Gnorc</span></p>
</a>
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="bifmvw" data-video-descrip="The Ice Cavern realm consists of a winding maze of icy caves and tunnels, all connecting to a single, massive cavern. There are plenty of guardrails and ramparts. Mist constantly rolls in through the pink and blue glowing caves. Above, the night sky is stretched out in an array of purple and blue, dotted with tiny white stars." data-video-title="Ice Cavern" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/bifmvw_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/ice_cavern_ps1.png" data-video-trope="Main/SlippySlideyIceWorld" data-video-tropename="Slippy-Slidey Ice World" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="VideoGame/SpyroTheDragon1998" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/ice_cavern_ps1.png">
<p><span class="bold">Ice Cavern</span></p>
</a>
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="s8za0b" data-video-descrip="Toasty was the very first boss in the Spyro the Dragon franchise." data-video-title="Toasty" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/s8za0b_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/s8za0b.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/WarmupBoss" data-video-tropename="Warm-Up Boss" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="VideoGame/SpyroTheDragon1998" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/s8za0b.jpg">
